# Technology Stack

## Core Framework

- **TanStack Start:** Full-stack React framework (latest stable)
- **React:** 19.x
- **TypeScript:** 5.7+
- **Build Tool:** Vite (via TanStack Start)
- **Package Manager:** Bun

## TanStack Start Specifics

### File-Based Routing

- Routes in `src/routes/`
- `__root.tsx` for root layout
- `index.tsx` for landing page
- API routes in `src/routes/api/` if needed

### Server Functions

- Use `createServerFn` for server-side logic (e.g., waitlist submission)
- Keep server functions minimal since no database

### SSR/SSG

- Prefer static generation where possible for performance
- SSR only where dynamic content is needed

## UI & Styling

### CSS Framework

- **Tailwind CSS:** 4.x with CSS-first configuration
- **Design Tokens:** CSS custom properties for theming

### Component Library

- **Shadcn UI:** For base components (Button, Input, Card, etc.)
- **Customization:** Heavy theming to match dark security aesthetic

### Icons

- **Tabler Icons React:** Consistent, clean icon set

### Animations

- **CSS Animations:** Preferred for simple transitions
- **Framer Motion:** For complex orchestrated animations
- Focus areas: Hero entrance, feature cards, progress indicators

### Typography

- **Display Font:** Cabinet Grotesk
- **Body Font:** Geist
- **Mono Font:** JetBrains Mono

## Code Highlighting

- **Shiki:** For syntax highlighting in code examples
- **Theme:** Custom dark theme matching site aesthetic

## Forms & Validation

- **TanStack Form:** For waitlist signup form
- **Zod:** Schema validation
- Keep forms minimal (email only for waitlist)

## External Services (Optional)

### Email/Waitlist

- **Resend:** For email collection

### Analytics (Optional)

- **Plausible:** Privacy-friendly analytics
- **Vercel Analytics:** If deploying to Vercel

## Development Tools

### Code Quality

- **Ultracite:** Linting and formatting
- **TypeScript:** Strict mode enabled

### Development

- **TanStack DevTools:** Router debugging
- **React DevTools:** Component inspection

## Deployment

### Recommended Platforms
- **Netlify**

### Build Output

- Static export where possible
- Edge functions for any server logic

## Project Structure

```
qauth-landing/
├── src/
│   ├── routes/
│   │   ├── __root.tsx      # Root layout, meta tags
│   │   ├── index.tsx       # Landing page
│   │   └── api/            # API routes (if needed)
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── ui/             # Shadcn components
│   │   ├── sections/       # Page sections
│   │   │   ├── hero.tsx
│   │   │   ├── features.tsx
│   │   │   ├── roadmap.tsx
│   │   │   ├── integration.tsx
│   │   │   ├── benefits.tsx
│   │   │   ├── waitlist.tsx
│   │   │   └── footer.tsx
│   │   └── shared/         # Shared components
│   │       ├── code-block.tsx
│   │       ├── feature-card.tsx
│   │       └── status-badge.tsx
│   ├── lib/
│   │   ├── utils.ts        # Utility functions
│   │   └── constants.ts    # Site constants
│   └── styles/
│       └── globals.css     # Global styles, Tailwind
├── public/
│   ├── fonts/              # Self-hosted fonts
│   └── og-image.png        # Open Graph image
├── app.config.ts           # TanStack Start config
├── tailwind.config.ts      # Tailwind configuration
└── package.json
```

